Graph Editor

Packages
org.grapheditor.editor In this packet and all its subpackages there is classes that have something to do with the grapheditor.
org.grapheditor.editor.exporters The classes in this package are used to export the graph to externial file formats.
org.grapheditor.editor.graph This package contains classes to represent the graph structure.
org.grapheditor.editor.importers This package contains classes that have something to do with export to externial file formats.
org.grapheditor.editor.listeners This package contains interfaces for listeners.
org.grapheditor.editor.menus The package contains menus used by the GraphEditorPane component.
org.grapheditor.editor.vertexrenders In this package there are classes that extend from the class VertexRender which is in the JGraph library and is an interface to get a component to render vertices.
org.grapheditor.gui This package contains classes that have something to do with the graphical user interface for the program.
org.grapheditor.gui.menus This package contains the menus that is in the main window.
org.grapheditor.gui.toolbars Here is classes for the program's toolbars with quick buttons.
org.grapheditor.properties This package contains classes that are used to manage the programs and graphs settings.
